The paper deals with improving the spectral efficiency of mmWave MIMO systems using analog precoding. This involves techniques related to information theory (cs.IT), communication systems (cs.COMM), millimeter wave communication (cs.MM), system engineering (cs.SY), and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
